		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Sounds like a made-up argument of a biased Saga fanboy who refuses to admit that the Super NES is like 10 times superior to his beloved Sega genesis in therms of graphics &amp; sound (sorry couldn't resist...)</div>
